CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 27, 1958, pg. 2, reads: "Landlord's Home - Alfred E. Davis, cited for Health Department regulation violations in his Homewood property in the 6800 block of Frankstown Ave., lives above at 7707 Baxter St. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two and one-half story house with cement staircase in front, 7707 Baxter Street, Homewood
